## โครงสร้างโปรเจกต์

```
BA_TOOL/
├── RUN.PY                    # Orchestrator: เริ่ม backend + frontend
├── .env                      # Environment variables 
├── backend/
│   ├── api/
│   │   └── main.py           # FastAPI app, routes, session management
│   ├── core/
│   │   ├── converter.py      # DataTypeConverter + byte anomaly detection
│   │   └── cache_store.py    # In-memory session cache
│   ├── parser/
│   │   └── sql_parser.py     # SQL DDL parser + FK validator
│   ├── exporter/
│   │   └── excel_exporter.py # XLSX / CSV export
│   ├── repository/
│   │   └── mapping_repo.py   # PostgreSQL: โหลด type mapping
│   └── config/
│       ├── db.py             # Connection pool management
│       └── logger.py         # Logging config
├── frontend/
│   ├── index.html            # Single-page UI
│   ├── script.js             # Frontend logic
│   └── style.css             # Styles (dark/light theme)
└── data/
    └── *.sql                 # ตัวอย่าง SQL files สำหรับทดสอบ
```

